40|$|The {{bachelor}} thesis {{analyzes the}} <b>agricultural</b> <b>insurance</b> in the Czech insurance market. It describes the occurrence and {{form of the}} risks in agriculture and <b>agricultural</b> <b>insurance</b> {{as one of the}} ways of the protection against them. It briefly describes the development of <b>agricultural</b> <b>insurance</b> in the territory of today's Czech Republic and after that the characteristics of the crop and livestock insurance in the last ten years. Another part of the work is focused on the government subsidies on <b>agricultural</b> <b>insurance</b> operated in the Czech Republic. The largest part of this bachelor thesis is focused on describing and comparing the insurance terms and conditions of the three major insurers in the market of <b>agricultural</b> <b>insurance</b> in the Czech Republic (České pojišťovna a. s., Generali Pojišťovna a. s., Agra pojišťovna) ...|$|R
